   t-fires-africa-and-the-amazon <p> During the summer of 2019, major
   fires have spread through Amazonia and central Africa. They have
   alerted the entire world to the need to manage forests and territories
   effectively. CIRAD is using its multi-disciplinary expertise and field
   experience to support local players in the fight against deforestation
   and degradation and promote forest landscape restoration. </p> Fri, 13
