   Expert Plantes Développement Durable (SEP2D) programme , funded by AFD,
   FFEM, MEAE, IRD and MNHN. the event, co-organized with Abomey-Calavi
   University, is open to the whole of the scientific community and to
   plant biodiversity management players and users. </p> Wed, 04 Sep 2019
